snippet.title: PlayStation - Mitsumete Knight R - Daibouken-hen (1998) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Mitsumete Knight R: Daibouken-hen is a Role-Playing game, developed and published by Konami, which was released in Japan in 1998.
